{"pageProps":{"post":{"attributes":{},"html":"<h1 id=\"saving-credentials-with-credential-managent-api\">Saving Credentials with Credential Managent API</h1>\n<p>At <code>Auth.js</code> we will update <code>postLogin</code> and <code>logout</code> adding the following algoritms:</p>\n<h2 id=\"post-login\">Post-Login</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-js\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// Credential Management API</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PasswordCredential</span> &amp;&amp; user.<span class=\"hljs-property\">password</span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">const</span> credential = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PasswordCredential</span>({\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">name</span>: user.<span class=\"hljs-property\">name</span>,\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">id</span>: user.<span class=\"hljs-property\">email</span>,\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">password</span>: user.<span class=\"hljs-property\">password</span>\n    });\n    navigator.<span class=\"hljs-property\">credentials</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">store</span>(credential);\n}\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"logout\">Logout</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-js\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-variable language_\">window</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PasswordCredential</span>) {\n            navigator.<span class=\"hljs-property\">credentials</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">preventSilentAccess</span>()\n        }\n</code></pre>\n","slug":"saving-credentials","title":"Saving Credentials","section":"Credential Management","icon":"passport","filePath":"/Users/firt/Library/Mobile Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/Trainings/FEM/Authentication/fullstack-authentication/lessons/03-credential-management/A-saving-credentials.md","nextSlug":"/authentication/lessons/credential-management/recovering-credentials","prevSlug":"/authentication/lessons/classic-login/calling-apis"}},"__N_SSG":true}